# Personal / machine-specific overrides
#
# Copy this file to `CLAUDE.local.md` (gitignored) and fill in your details.
# The install script does this automatically if `CLAUDE.local.md` is missing.

## Working areas (this machine)
- Personal projects: ~/Developer/Personal
- Work projects:     ~/Developer/<org>

## Identity
- Git author name / email: <Your Name> <you@example.com>

## Investigation / OSINT specifics (optional — delete if N/A)
- Isolated browser profile: <path to hardened profile>
- Egress: <proxy> via <extension>, under <VPN>
- Launch alias: <alias>

## Other local overrides
- Local dev ports, secret *locations* (paths only, never values), machine quirks.
